title: TikTok Tuesday #SwifTok
description:
It’s time for our Tuesday meeting and let’s go where all of the Swifties gather and share.. Yes, we are busy scrolling and posting and theorizing on TikTok too.. These are some cool ones that we have discovered, interesting theories that we are buying into, and someone covered our versions of All Too Well! WOW!

What theories are you buying into? Who should we be following? And what did we miss?
